title: 586. Reaction to MNF Games + Trey Lance on Players He Models His Game After
itunes:title: 586. Reaction to MNF Games + Trey Lance on Players He Models His Game After
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks are back with a special new episode. To start off, the guys give their takeaway from the Monday Night Football game between the Steelers and Giants (1:55). Next, the pair give their thoughts from the second Monday Night Football game as the Titans faced off vs. the Broncos and the duo also look at the AFC West (8:32). Then, North Dakota State QB Trey Lance joins to talk about how he's working on his skills during the pandemic, NFL players he models his game after and the culture at North Dakota State (15:01).
